{"tid":61773,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"法國喺外地有啲活動得自己一個就會好想走","createTime":"2016-12-31T13:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T13:34:03.000Z","uid":16951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e362ba46b295c58055d3561bbc3017a78d7013ec","tid":61773,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:13:53.000Z","msg":"先利申：我是巴打 有囡囡的<br />\n嚟京阪旅行 原本係同家姐一齊 佢今晚要飛走先<br />\n啱啱去左住吉大社 自己一個 <br />\n咁諗住單機都好 影下相啦<br />\n跟住行行下都發現大多數人都一pair pair 屋企人又好 情侶又好 <br />\n喺呢一刻先諗返起以前單身嗰陣點解唔會呢啲日子出街 <br />\n因為同其他人有對比囉<br />\n因為有野想同人分享 隔離都無人囉<br />\n因為融入唔到囉<br />\n唉 我而家就返緊阿波座間酒店沖涼睇陣漫畫plan下聽日行程就瞓<br />\n希望各位巴絲今日留喺屋企又好 出街都好<br />\n都會開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caea9b336b526c7313be54ae4927bea11ca32ce8","tid":61773,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}